==English==
===Adjective===
'''cyclic'''
#Characterized by, or moving in [[cycle]]s, or [[happening]] at [[regular]] [[interval]]s
#* The weather had a '''cyclic''' pattern of rain and sun
#{{chemistry}} Of a [[compound]] having [[chain]]s of [[atom]]s [[arrange]]d in a [[ring]]
#* Benzene and cyclohexane are both '''cyclic''' compounds
#(''botany'') Having parts arranged in a [[whorl]]
#(''mathematics'') ''(of a group)'' being [[generate]]d by only one [[element]]
